      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i think something weird is happening to me. lately i've been able to process information way faster than usual. like, i can read a page and immediately grasp the whole concept without even rereading. it feels like my brain is literally running on a different frequency. i was reading about cosmic radiation and how it can affect cellular structures... do you think it's possible some kind of environmental trigger could actually physically change how my neurons fire?",
